title: Wilson faces road test at Manheim Township
text:
Wilson faces road test at Manheim Township Shane Dantzler back in the lineup as Bulldogs approach 100% Published: 6:38 PM EDT Oct 21, 2015 Updated: 11:43 PM EDT Oct 21, 2015 Wilson healthier heading into showdown with Blue Streaks SPRING TOWNSHIP - 
There are a handful of de facto league championship games on the gridiron over the final three weeks of the regular season. You could say Wilson kicks off that stretch Friday night at Manheim Township. 
It's a showdown of 6-1 teams. The winner will be the only remaining league unbeaten within Section I of the Lancaster-Lebanon League. 
The Bulldogs are getting healthy. That includes the return of Shanze Dantzler last week, although Tommy O'Brien did most of the legwork against Conestoga Valley. Quick Clicks
